title: Caitlyn Jenner Warns President Trump: 'We'll See You In Court' - Fox Nation
text:
Caitlyn Jenner Warns President Trump: 'We'll See You In Court' Published February 24, 2017 AP 
By CAITLIN YILEK, Washington Examiner 
Transgender reality television star Caitlyn Jenner is calling the Trump administration's decision to repeal guidelines on public school bathrooms for transgender students "a disaster."
